metadata.description: Thinking big needs big balls! Bigballs movement stands for a community of people that engage each other to reach their biggest dreams. Including inventors, startups, artists, investors and visionaries: every kind of big thinking mind finds its place in this environment and gets support in its unique vision. Each of the 10.000 unique NFT tokens acts as a member ticket to this exclusive club of doers. Show the world your balls and become a part of thr Big Balls Movement. www.bigballsmovement.com
